org.diylc.core.annotations
Annotation Type EditableProperty

@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface EditableProperty

Used to annotate editable component property. Editable property XYZ must have both getter and setter named getXYZ and setXYZ respectively and this annotation must be placed on the getter method.

Author:
Branislav Stojkovic

name

public abstract java.lang.String name
Returns property name. If left blank property name will be extracted from the getter name, e.g. getter getXYZ will induce property name XYZ.
Default value is blank.

Returns:
Default:
""
